    "name": "钢之战骑ARMIS",
    "steam_appid": 3214220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/4355dc8b1668a00774675309f12a93b2.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>「钢之战骑ARMIS」是一款让玩家扮演ARMIS（Advanced Robotic Mechanized Interceptor System）驾驶员，在戏剧性战场中生存的机器人游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将化身为反抗军的一员，经历分为五个部分的故事情节并生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的敌人不仅包括像弹幕一样直线攻击的敌军，还会有同样由驾驶员操控的敌方ARMIS登场。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏玩法非常简单，但为了对抗敌方ARMIS，强化您的ARMIS至关重要。通过积累经验值来提升等级，并从随机出现的强化装备中选择，让你的ARMIS独具特色，逐步成长为强大的战斗机器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/78bf98749602c1c70950ac3658fdc56b.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/cdf51b607f0aaf34b89366941a70c6c0.poster.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/cdf51b607f0aaf34b89366941a70c6c0.webm?t=1761727654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/cdf51b607f0aaf34b89366941a70c6c0.mp4?t=1761727654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极限强化的 ARMIS甚至能够横扫一大群敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请用您喜欢的配置，尽情体验击溃无数敌人的爽快感吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/0f256593d73e2137f28459a5b3a9e4c2.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/68f37a9b3a09be37eeab549a0deaacba.poster.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=319 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/68f37a9b3a09be37eeab549a0deaacba.webm?t=1761727654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>本作的故事分为五章，仿佛让人置身于经典热血机器人动画之中，每一章的主人公都不同。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请体验他们怀抱的情感与立场交织而成的热血故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/e673653cd69d8f7bccd12faaf4221a09.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/14cecdff60f24de96fee45cad5d32cb7.poster.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/14cecdff60f24de96fee45cad5d32cb7.webm?t=1761727654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/14cecdff60f24de96fee45cad5d32cb7.mp4?t=1761727654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作中设有能够无缝切换至“纵向射击模式”的场景。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的游戏体验之间的无缝衔接，为您带来与传统轻度Roguelike动作游戏截然不同的全新体验。<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214220/extras/b63098bdd2c42357ca149587dd5295a6.avif?t=1761727654\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p>",
